# # additional tools # #
########################

# cutecom: help to monitor a serial port communication
- install using Ubuntu Software Centre

# terminator: help to handle many terminal windows at time efficiently
- install using Ubuntu Software Centre

# gedit plug-in: make gedit be capable of doing programming tasks more efficient
- via command "sudo apt-get install gedit-plugins"
- source: https://help.gnome.org/users/gedit/unstable/gedit-plugin-guide.html.en
- setting up a preference
    - in "Editor"
        - set "Tap Width" = 4
        - check "insert space instead of tab"
        - check "automatic indentation"
        - uncheck two items in "File Saving"
    - in "Plugins"
        - enable "code comment"
